I guard.

46
00:03:50,827 --> 00:03:52,462
Lien!

47
00:03:52,462 --> 00:03:53,797
Kay!

48
00:03:53,797 --> 00:03:55,332
Llew!

49
00:03:55,332 --> 00:03:57,000
Margal!

50
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:59,870
♪

51
00:03:59,870 --> 00:04:02,739
Those four cards
bumped him up to 35,000.

52
00:04:02,739 --> 00:04:05,275
Should be more than enough
for him to stop Ren.

53
00:04:05,275 --> 00:04:08,111
That's right,
he'll survive it...I think.

54
00:04:08,111 --> 00:04:10,013
‐You think?
‐You think?

55
00:04:10,013 --> 00:04:12,149
So, in the end,
all you were capable

56
00:04:12,149 --> 00:04:14,551
