I got a heal trigger.

62
00:04:24,127 --> 00:04:28,832
Adding 5,000 power
to Phantom Blaster Overlord.

63
00:04:28,832 --> 00:04:31,902
And, of course, I recover one.

64
00:04:31,902 --> 00:04:35,038
I really don't like
the way this looks.

65
00:04:35,038 --> 00:04:36,807
The power boost,
it should have gone

66
00:04:36,807 --> 00:04:40,877
